\id 1TH - Nchane
\h 1 Tɛsalonika
\toc1 Ŋwa wù fwe wu Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ kintaashɛ ki Tɛsalonika le
\toc2 1 Tɛsalonika
\toc3 1Tɛ
\mt2 Ŋwa wù fwe wu Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ kintaashɛ ki
\mt1 Tɛsalonika le
\imt1 Fiɛɛ fì le a Ŋwa wu Tɛsalonika wù fwe wunɛ le
\ip Tɛsalonika gɛ̀ bee kilaantɛŋ kimi a kimbe ki woŋ wù Masɛdonia le, a Bol gɛ̀ kɛ kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ yo. Fi gɛ̀ baaŋ she gɛ no kintaashɛ kinɛ gɛ̀ kɛ gɛ, Bajuu mo bo kɛ bo banɛ Bol bo bɛɛne kindoŋ bɛ wu. Bol mo wu saŋ ŋwa wù fwe wunɛ fɛ bamii ba Kletu ba Tɛsalonika le ki wu fɛ̂ muntele muboo yûfe, wu gê bo lɛ̂me bo tɛ̂ɛme.
\iot Bikwɛɛ bi mwɛɛ mù le a Ŋwa wunɛ le
\io1 1:1 Fɛŋkɛɛ
\io1 1:2–3:13 Bol yu njoŋ wu ka wu bɛɛŋsɛ bamii ba mbɛmɛ
\io1 4:1-12 Ntefɛ kune kinche ki bamii ba le ba Kletu
\io1 4:13–5:11 Ntefɛ kune no Kletu lé wu gê wu kâasɛ wu tô
\io1 5:12-22 Ntefɛ yi fɛkimɛsɛ
\io1 5:23-28 Kimɛsɛ
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Le mɛ wù Bol, nle besa Sila mo Timoti. Nsaŋe ŋwa wunɛ fɛ kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ ba a kilaantɛŋ kì Tɛsalonika kì le ki taashɛ ki nyume bɛ Nyo wù Chii yi Tada Jiso Kletu le.
\p Nyo wù Chiji wese besabɛŋ dûnyɛ fitele fì joŋe fɛ bɛŋ le, wu ka wu nyâ bɛŋ bɛ muntele mù nyiɛgee.
\s1 Bol nya kiyone fɛ Nyo le yi kintaashɛ // ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ ki Tɛsalonika le
\p 
\v 2 Bee to bee nyaa kiyone Nyo le segechii kune bɛŋ bachii, bee buune segechii bee gɛɛde bɛŋ a buunɛ chesa le.
\v 3 Sege bee le a Nyo wù le Chiji wese besabɛŋ fwe, bee tu be kwaji gee chinɛ chì bude yi fitele fì bɛŋ leese yi Kletu le bɛ lɛme chinɛ chì bude yi kiŋkoŋɛ kena le mo shɛ́ŋ yì bɛŋ kaane yì bude yi njiŋɛ wù bɛŋ jiiŋe fwe yi Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso Kletu le.
\p 
\v 4 Booŋ ba bwee wese ba Nyo koŋe, bee kee lɛ Nyo le wu cha wa bɛŋ.
\v 5 Bee kee noo nje saaka wù joŋe wù bee gɛ̀ too bɛ wu fɛ bɛŋ le, gɛ wu gɛ̀ to nyu bɛ njɛmɛ maa gɛ. Wu gɛ̀ to tɛ bɛ bvuŋga bvù jade fɛ Kiyo ki Yuude le, bee kee chuule lɛ saaka wuyu le nchiɛɛŋ. Bɛŋ kee kfuu chi bamii ba gɛ̀ bee bee sege bee gɛ̀ chee a bɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ nje bɛŋ.
\v 6 Bɛŋ tu bɛŋ bege besa ba Tada nje bɛŋ gɛ̀ fi saaka wuyu bɛ kinlaŋye kì jade fɛ Kiyo ki Yuude le mo no bɛŋ gɛ̀ fede yi ŋgɛ wù baaŋ le.
\v 7 Noo, bɛŋ mo bɛŋ tu bamii ba bamii ba mbɛmɛ bachii ba a bimbe bì Masɛdonia le mo bì Akɛya le bo jôde njiŋɛ fɛ bo le.
\v 8 Njɛme nɛ nje gɛ mɛ gɛh jɛ yi Tada yi saane fɛ bɛŋ le yi jiɛnyi a bimbe bì Masɛdonia le mo bì Akɛya le gɛ. Saaka wù kune fitele fiena fì bɛŋ leese yi Nyo le, le fi jiɛnyɛ wa tɛ manjuu le manchii. Noo gɛ ntaŋ ka nyume yu wù besabɛŋ jɛ̂me fiɛɛ kune fi gɛ.
\v 9 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ bamii bayu kibɛɛ le bo sɛɛŋ kune no bɛŋ gɛ̀ fi bee a bɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ, mo no bɛŋ gɛ̀ chinɛ banyo le bɛŋ tu bɛ Nyo, ki bɛŋ lɛ̂ne wa nyu Nyo wù nchiɛɛŋ le wù kɛme kinche.
\v 10 Bo sɛɛŋ tɛ no bɛŋ chiɛɛne Mwa ye wù lé wu gê wu jâ fɛwe wu tô. Mwa ye wunɛ le wu wù gɛ̀ bu yi kwe le, nyume Jiso wù bvuse besabɛŋ chiaaŋ yi shɛ́ŋ yi Nyo yì bɛɛne yì wu lé wu gê wu dûnyɛ bamii le.
\c 2
\s1 Bol jɛmɛ kune lɛme che chi Tɛsalonika
\p 
\v 1 Booŋ ba bwee wese, bɛŋ kibɛɛ kêe lɛ gɛ jigɛ chì bee gɛ̀ la a bɛŋ le gɛ̀ lɛsɛ achiji gɛ.
\v 2 Mo no bɛŋ kêe lɛ bamii gɛ̀ nyaa ŋgɛ bee le bo ka nyuse bɛ bee a kilaantɛŋ kì Filibi le, bee gɛ̀ kaane gɛh shɛ́ŋ a bvuŋga bvu Nyo wese le, ki bee fejɛ saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo bɛŋ le mo no bamii bamu gɛ̀ chidɛ bee wesee nɛ.
\v 3 Gɛ saaka wù bee gɛ̀ feeji bee lɛge bɛŋ yu gɛ̀ bee bɛ jialɛ kɛnɛ bɛ ŋkwajɛ wumu wù befe kɛnɛ bee goone ki bee lɛ̂ɛ lo bɛ bɛŋ gɛ.
\v 4 Geenɛ no Nyo le wu yɛŋ lɛ bee le be kojɛ bamii ba wu nyâ saaka wù joŋe wunɛ chiaaŋ yiboo le, noo bee mo be feeji. Gɛ bee feeji lɛ ye jôŋe nyume bamii gɛ. Bee feeji lɛ yi jôŋe nyume Nyo wù taade muntele mwesa.
\v 5 No bɛŋ kee lɛ bee gɛ̀ baaŋ a yu gɛ be tôo bɛ jɛ́ ki bee yɛne kɛnɛ ki bee tɛyɛ fiɛɛ fɛ jii ki bee jî fiɛɛ chiaaŋ yene le gɛ. Finɛ nyume fiɛɛ fì Nyo lɛme a bee fwe.
\v 6 Gɛ bee baaŋ be goone ki be kɛ̂mɛ mbɛɛŋsɛ wumu fɛ muh le kɛnɛ wù jade fɛ bɛŋ le kɛnɛ fɛ bamii bamu le gɛ. Gɛ̀ bee kijusɛ kesa njɛ booŋ ba ntuŋ ba Kletu lɛ ki bee bîide mwɛɛ, lɛ bɛŋ gêe fɛ bee le
\v 7 Bee gɛ̀ bee fiesa nyiɛgee a bɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ njɛ bwee mwa wù jiiŋe fɛ booŋ be le.
\v 8 Noo, bee mo bee jo bɛŋ ye le chuule bɛ kiŋkoŋɛ, gɛ bee gɛ nya bɛŋ nyume bɛ saaka wù joŋe wu Nyo maa gɛ, geenɛ bee nya tɛ bikwɛɛ biɛsa bɛŋ le nje bɛŋ gɛ̀ bee wa a muntele mwesa le baaŋ.
\p 
\v 9 Booŋ ba bwee wese, gɛ bɛŋ kwaji tɛ lɛme chesa bɛ mbunyɛ wese gɛ. Bee gɛ̀ lɛne antaŋ bɛ fɛnshɛ wu lɛ keefɛ bee gɛɛ bvujijɛ yi muh mu bɛŋ le no bee gɛ̀ feeji saaka wù joŋe wù wu Nyo fɛ bɛŋ le gɛ.
\v 10 Bɛŋ kibɛɛ mo Nyo taŋlo bɛŋ bɛɛ jiŋ yi nsa wese lɛ kinche kesa fɛ bɛŋ bamii ba mbɛmɛ le, gɛ̀ bee kì yuude nyume kì chaaŋ ki kɛme gɛ jialɛ chimi gɛ.
\v 11 Bɛŋ kee tɛ no bee gɛ̀ gee bɛ bɛŋ njɛ no chiji mwa to wu gee bɛ booŋ be.
\v 12 Bee gɛ̀ yufe muntele mwɛna, bee loji bɛŋ, bee toone lɛ bɛŋ chêe kinche kì Nyo goone. Nyume Nyo wù tɛŋe bɛŋ lɛ bɛŋ lêe bvunfoŋ bwe le bɛ bvukugɛ bwe.
\p 
\v 13 Bee to bee nyaa kiyone Nyo le nje finɛ fì le lɛ sege bee gɛ̀ to bɛ jɛ yi Nyo fɛ bɛŋ le, bɛŋ gɛ̀ fi jɛ yiyu gɛh no yi gɛ̀ bee lɛ le jɛ yi Nyo, nyume gɛ jɛ yi muh gɛ. Nyume yi yì lɛne ye yene le, bɛŋ ba le bamii ba mbɛmɛ.
\v 14 Booŋ ba bwee wese bɛŋ kêe lɛ fiɛɛ fì gɛ̀ kooshɛ bɛ bintaashɛ bi bamii ba mbɛmɛ ba Nyo bì le bi bɛɛŋ Kletu Jiso le a kimbe ki Judia le, gɛ̀ kooshɛ tɛ bɛ bɛŋ. Bɛŋ gɛ̀ yɛŋ tɛ baŋgɛ chiaaŋ yi bamii bena ba woŋ le gɛh yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no bo gɛ̀ yɛŋ chiaaŋ yi Bajuu baboo le.
\v 15 Bajuu banɛ le bo bò gɛ̀ yuuyɛ Tada Jiso. Nyume bo bò gɛ̀ yuuyi bamii ba ntuŋ ba Nyo. Nyume bo bò gɛ̀ kuŋɛ bɛ bee abo nɛ. Bo gee noo Nyo yuge gɛ njoŋ bɛ bo gɛ. Bo banɛ bamii bachii,
\v 16 no bo baŋe je bee le ki be jɛme bamii ba le gɛ Bajuu le gɛ wu lɛ bo bonɛ. Bo gee noo segechii bimbefɛ biboo yiise bi bɛɛne. Shɛ́ŋ yi Nyo yì bɛɛne nyume yi to wa yi bo le mɛɛse.
\s1 Bol tu wu kɛme kiŋkoŋɛ ki wu ka wu yɛ̂ŋ bamii ba mbɛmɛ ba Tɛsalonika
\p 
\v 17 Booŋ ba bwee wese, no besabɛŋ chi gasɛ bee moŋ wa wesee bee kɛme kiŋkoŋɛ baaŋ lɛ bee yɛŋ bɛŋ le ajii mo nyume baaŋ gɛh yi kife ki shige le, no besabɛŋ chi gasɛ. Besabɛŋ le be gasɛ gɛh nyume bɛ ajii. Besabɛŋ baaŋ gasɛ gɛ a fitele le gɛ.
\v 18 Bee goone ki be kaasɛ be to a bɛŋ le. Mɛ wù Bol kibɛɛ nle mmoŋ wa chikɛ le chikɛ le, geenɛ Sataŋ baŋe gɛh bee.
\v 19 Bee kɛme ntaŋ ki bee to nɛ nje fiɛɛ fì taŋlo bee jiiŋe fwe yi fi le, kɛnɛ bvujoŋɛ bwesa bɛ gvune chesa chì bee le be ge be chîaase ye yu fwe a Tada wese wù Jiso sege wu lé wu gê wu kâasɛ wu tô le nyu la? Gɛ nyume bɛŋ gɛ?
\v 20 Le bɛŋ ba le mbɛɛŋsɛ bɛ bvujoŋɛ bwesa.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Noo, no bee gɛ̀ yɛŋ lɛ fi le fi gha wa, bee chu ntaŋ ki bee shɛɛ jiŋ Atɛŋ bee maa,
\v 2 bee mo be tuŋ Timoti wù mwa bwee wese besabɛŋ wù besa bo lɛne Nyo le yi saaka wù joŋe wù kune Kletu le. Bee gɛ̀ tuŋ lɛ wu tô wu lêesɛ bɛŋ, wu teefɛ bɛŋ yi fitele fì bɛŋ le bɛŋ leese yi Kletu le,
\v 3 lɛ keefɛ baŋgɛ banɛ ka bo shiŋshɛ muh mu bɛŋ le gɛ. Bɛŋ kibɛɛ kee lo lɛ baŋgɛ le wa fiɛɛ fiesa besabɛŋ.
\v 4 Bɛŋ kee lɛ sege bee gɛ̀ bee besabɛŋ bee gɛ̀ sɛɛŋ bɛŋ le baaŋ lo lɛ besabɛŋ le be yɛ̂ŋ baŋgɛ. Nyume gɛh yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no fi le fi kooshɛ wa bɛŋ kee.
\v 5 Le fiɛɛ fì gɛ̀ ge mɛ lɛ ndoo n'yɛŋ lɛ fi le fi gha wa, mɛ mo ntuŋ Timoti ki ŋkɛɛ no mbɛmɛ wene le, nje ŋgɛ ŋkɛme nfaaŋ lɛ taŋlo muh wɛɛ wù mone bamii le wu moŋ wa bɛŋ wu ge lɛme chichii chì bee lɛŋ fɛ bɛŋ le chi tu achiji.
\s1 Timoti nya saaka wù kune mbɛmɛ bamii ba Tɛsalonika le
\p 
\v 6 Geenɛ mɛɛse Timoti le wu to fɛ bɛŋ le, wu kaasɛ wu tu jiŋ fɛ bee le, wu sɛɛŋ saaka wù joŋe wu kune fitele fì bɛŋ leese yi Kletu le bɛ no bɛŋ dûunyi kiŋkoŋɛ fɛ bamii le. Wu le wu sɛɛŋ tɛ no bɛŋ kwaji bee chuule bɛŋ ka kɛme kiŋkoŋɛ ki bɛŋ yɛ̂ŋ bee le no bee kɛme tɛ kiŋkoŋɛ ki be yɛ̂ŋ bɛŋ le.
\v 7 Nje finɛ booŋ ba bwee wese, yi nsaasɛ bɛ baŋgɛ ba bee kɛme le, shɛ́ŋ jiɛɛ bee kune bɛŋ baaŋ nje fitele fì bɛŋ leese yi Kletu le.
\v 8 Mɛɛse bee le be yɛnɛ nje bɛŋ lɛ̂me bɛŋ tɛ̂ɛme bena ba Tada.
\v 9 Noo, bee nyâa kiyone Nyo le baaŋ nje bɛŋ. Bee nyâa nje njoŋ wù bee yuge a Nyo wese besabɛŋ fwe nje bɛŋ.
\v 10 Bee buune chiɛɛŋ antaŋ bɛ fɛnshɛ lɛ taŋlo bee ka be yɛŋ bɛŋ le ajii, wu lɛ bee nya bɛŋ bɛ fiɛɛ fì baaŋ fi fuge yi mbɛmɛ wene le.
\p 
\v 11 Bee buune lɛ Nyo wù le Chiji wese besabɛŋ kibɛɛ mo Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso gwênyɛ je lɛ bee to fɛ bɛŋ le.
\v 12 Bee buune tɛ lɛ Tada ge kiŋkoŋɛ kena kûu ki gɛ̂ɛne fwe no bɛŋ koŋe bikwɛɛ biɛna bɛ bamii bachii, yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no bee koŋe bɛŋ.
\v 13 Bee buune noo, wu lɛ wu ge muntele mwɛna tɛɛme, bɛŋ nyume jialɛ sɛŋ, bɛŋ yuude a Nyo wù le Chiji wese besabɛŋ fwe sege Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso too bɛ bamii ba le be bachii.
\c 4
\s1 Kinche kì Nyo koŋe
\p 
\v 1 Ki mɛɛse, booŋ ba bwee wese, bee lɛge bɛŋ, bee kude lo chiaaŋ njɛ bamii ba le bo taashɛ yi Tada Jiso le, no bɛŋ gɛ̀ yɛyɛ a bee le, no bɛŋ kɛme ki bɛŋ chêe no Nyo koŋe, nyume gɛh noo, no bɛŋ chee mɛɛse, bɛŋ gêe gɛh noo bɛŋ gɛɛne lo fwe fwe.
\v 2 Bɛŋ kee wa nteefɛ yi bee gɛ̀ nya bɛŋ le a bvuŋga bvu Tada Jiso le.
\v 3 Fiɛɛ fì Nyo koŋe le lɛ bɛŋ yûude. Keefɛ bɛŋ jâŋe kinjaŋ gɛ.
\v 4 Muh wu mumwaa wu mumwaa bɛŋ le kɛme ki wu kêe ki wu jîji ye ye le a je yì yuude le, yi kɛme ŋgvunɛ.\f + \fr 4:4\ft Kɛnɛ lɛ, “Muh wu mumwaa wu mumwaa bɛŋ le kɛme ki wu kêe no wu kɛ̂me kwɛɛ a je yì yuude le, yi kɛme ŋgvunɛ.”\f*
\v 5 Keefɛ ye yi muh yûfe gɛh lo gɛ, yi fuu njɛ yi muh wu kituŋ ki kee gɛ Nyo gɛ.
\v 6 Keefɛ muh gê kimbefɛ kɛnɛ wu gê jialɛ muh bɛ mwa bwee yi saaka wuyu wunɛ le gɛ. Bee gɛ̀ jɛmɛ wa bee chiisɛ lo bɛŋ le baaŋ lo lɛ Tada lé wu gê wu nôŋ ŋgɛ yi bamii ba gee mwɛɛ munɛ le munchii.
\v 7 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ gɛ Nyo gɛ̀ tɛŋe besabɛŋ lɛ besabɛŋ chêe nyume kinche ki nyiɛŋ lɛ gɛ. Wu gɛ̀ tɛŋe besabɛŋ lɛ bee chêe kinche kì yuude.
\v 8 Fi mo fi nyume lɛ mo yɛɛŋ wù le wu faŋ ki wu yû nteefɛ chinɛ, tu gɛ wu faŋ ki wu yû nyume muh wu wuŋ le gɛ. Wu faŋ ki wu yû nyume Nyo wù nyaa Kiyo ke ki Yuude bɛŋ le.
\p 
\v 9 Fi kune kiŋkoŋɛ ki bɛŋ kɛ̂mɛ fɛ booŋ ba bwee bena ba mbɛmɛ le, gɛ fiɛɛ ka baaŋ yu fì bee ka be saŋe kune fifiɛɛ fɛ bɛŋ le gɛ. Finɛ le fiɛɛ fì bɛŋ kibɛɛ le Nyo gɛ̀ yɛyɛ wa bɛŋ no taŋlo bɛŋ koŋe bikwɛɛ biɛna.
\v 10 Yi nchiɛɛŋ le, bɛŋ koŋe wa booŋ ba bwee bena bachii ba a kimbe kì Masɛdonia le. Geenɛ booŋ ba bwee wese, bee ka teefe bɛŋ lɛ bɛŋ gêe gɛh noo bɛŋ gɛ̂ɛne lo fwe fwe.
\v 11 Bɛŋ moŋ lɛ bɛŋ chêe kinche kì nyiɛgee, keefɛ bɛŋ lêese jwe fɛ mwɛɛ mu bamii le gɛ. Bɛŋ lɛ̂ne bɛ chiaaŋ yene no bee gɛ̀ teefɛ bɛŋ.
\v 12 Noo bamii ba akfuuŋ mo bo nyaa ŋgvunɛ fɛ bɛŋ le, bɛŋ gɛ ka bɛŋ chîɛɛne muh mu yi fiɛɛ le gɛ.
\s1 Kune kife kì Tada lé wu gê wu kâasɛ wu to
\p 
\v 13 Booŋ ba bwee wese, gɛ bee goone lɛ bɛŋ nyume yi kijibɛ le kune bamii ba le ba kweeyɛ wa gɛ. Bee goone lɛ bɛŋ kɛɛ, wu lɛ keefɛ bɛŋ nyûme yii yii njɛ bamii ba jiiŋe gɛ fwe yi bvujoŋɛ bvu too le gɛ.
\v 14 Besabɛŋ le be bɛɛŋ lɛ Jiso gɛ̀ bee wu kwe wu kaasɛ wu bu yi kwe le, le gɛh yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no Nyo lé wu gê wu kâasɛ wu chvûu Jiso jiŋ bɛ bamii ba gɛ̀ kweeyɛ bo nyume bo taashɛ bɛ wu.
\v 15 Bee jɛme finɛ bee bii gɛh nyu jɛ yi Tada le, lɛ gɛ besabɛŋ ba shɛshi ajiŋ ba lé ba gê ba nyûme yu yi kife ki Tada lé wu gê wu tôo le, gɛ besabɛŋ nyume bee sa fwe a bamii ba le bo kweeyɛ wa le gɛ.
\v 16 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ Tada kibɛɛ lé wu gê wu jâ fɛwe wu shîide wu tôo wu wânɛ fɛwɛɛwe bɛ jɛ yì tɛɛme, kikwɛɛ ki banchɛndaa ba Nyo jâŋe tɛ, soŋ yi Nyo jɛ̂me. Bamii ba gɛ̀ kweeyɛ wa bo nyume bo taashɛ wa bɛ ba Kletu ya bo bu fwe.
\v 17 Noo Nyo mo wu chufɛ besabɛŋ ba lé ba shɛ̂ɛ ba nyûme yu mo bo taashɛ yi kimbɛ le bee gɛɛŋ be tasɛ bɛ Tada yi kibvulɛ le. Besabɛŋ bɛ Tada mo be nyume segechii.
\v 18 Noo bɛŋ mo bɛŋ jîɛɛse fitele fì muh bɛ muh bɛ njɛmɛ wunɛ.
\c 5
\s1 No taŋlo muh chîɛɛne nto wu Tada
\p 
\v 1 Booŋ ba bwee wese, kune kife bɛ juu chi nto wu Tada, gɛ fi nyume lɛ ba ka ba saŋ lo fiɛɛ kune fifiɛɛ fɛ bɛŋ le gɛ.
\v 2 Bɛŋ kibɛɛ kee lo chuule lɛ juu chi nto wu Tada lé chi gê chi nyûme njɛ chi choŋ antaŋ.
\v 3 Sege bamii lé bo gê bo dûu lɛ, “Nyiɛgee le yu, fiɛɛ nyume gɛ yu fì muh ka wu faane gɛ”, ŋgɛ mo wu jaŋe wu gwe yi bo le njɛ lume fɛ chi ja chi to yi kwɛse wù le bɛ fwe le, je gɛ ka yi nyume yu yi bo legɛ gɛ.
\v 4 Geenɛ booŋ ba bwee wese, gɛ bɛŋ nyume fiena yi kijibɛ le, wù juu chiyu lé chi jâ gɛh nɛ chi tô fɛ bɛŋ le njɛ choŋ gɛ.
\v 5 Njɛme nɛ nje bɛŋ bachii le bamii ba n'yuu, bɛŋ nyume bamii ba fɛnshɛ. Gɛ besabɛŋ nyume bamii ba antaŋ kɛnɛ ba le yi kijibɛ le gɛ.
\v 6 Noo, keefɛ besabɛŋ lefe no bamii bamu lefe gɛ. Besabɛŋ nyûme we bɛ bvufee bwesa fo bvuchii.
\v 7 Bamii ba lefe to bo lefe nyume antaŋ, bamii ba mbvuuŋ koode bo, mo to mo koode bo nyume antaŋ.
\v 8 Geenɛ, no besabɛŋ le fiesa bamii ba fɛnshɛ, besabɛŋ nyume bɛ bvufee bwesa fo bvuchii. Besabɛŋ jô mbɛmɛ bɛ kiŋkoŋɛ mo nyûme njɛ kichwa ki jɛŋ kì bee le be bôoŋ bee baŋɛ gvúu yese besabɛŋ yu, bee jô tɛ njiŋɛ wù besabɛŋ jiiŋe fwe yi mbvusɛ le wu nyûme njɛ kifo ki jɛŋ kì bee booŋ.
\v 9 Bɛŋ kêe lɛ gɛ Nyo gɛ̀ cha besabɛŋ wu gɛɛ lɛ wu dûnyɛ nyu shɛ́ŋ ye yì bɛɛne besabɛŋ le gɛ. Wu gɛ̀ cha lɛ besabɛŋ kɛme nyu mbvusɛ fede yi Tada wese besabɛŋ wu Jiso Kletu le.
\v 10 Jiso Kletu le wu wù gɛ̀ kwe nje besabɛŋ, wu lɛ kɛnɛ besabɛŋ le yu, kɛnɛ besabɛŋ le be kwe, besabɛŋ nyume gɛh bɛ wu.
\v 11 Noo, bɛŋ mo bɛŋ yûfe muntele mu muh lɛ muh, bɛŋ jôone tɛ muh lɛ muh no bɛŋ gee.
\s1 Nteefɛ yì fɛkimɛsɛ bɛ n'yɛsɛ
\p 
\v 12 Booŋ ba bwee wese, bee lɛge lo bɛŋ lɛ bɛŋ ŋgvûune bamii ba lɛne bo ka jiiŋe fɛ bɛŋ le yi saaka wu Tada le bo ka teefe bɛŋ.
\v 13 Bɛŋ dûunyi ŋgvunɛ bo le chuule yi kiŋkoŋɛ le nje lɛme chiboo. Bɛŋ kɛ̂me tɛ kinche kì nyiɛgee abɛŋ ntɛnɛɛ.
\v 14 Bee ka lɛge tɛ bɛŋ booŋ ba bwee wese lɛ bɛŋ têefe bamii ba laame gɛh lo, bɛŋ yûfe muntele mu bamii ba kɛme njaŋ, bɛŋ fîih tɛ bamii ba wɛɛyi. Bɛŋ kâane shɛ́ŋ bɛ bamii bachii.
\v 15 Bɛŋ yɛ̂ne lɛ keefɛ muh chvûse kimbefɛ bɛ kimbefɛ gɛ. Bɛŋ gôone segechii ki bɛŋ gêe nyume mwɛɛ mù njoŋe fɛ bikwɛɛ biɛna le mo fɛ bamii le bachii.
\v 16 Bɛŋ lâŋeye segechii,
\v 17 bɛŋ bûune kife le kichii,
\v 18 bɛŋ nyâa kiyone Nyo le yi fiɛɛ le fichii fi kooshi. Finɛ fiɛɛ le fì Nyo goone fɛ bɛŋ ba le yi Kletu Jiso le.
\v 19 Keefɛ bɛŋ chîde lɛme chi Kiyo ki Yuude gɛ.
\v 20 Keefɛ bɛŋ lâase bantuŋ ba Nyo ba bamii be teede gɛ.
\v 21 Bɛŋ tâade mwɛɛ munchii, bɛŋ jôde mù njoŋe bɛŋ lɛme yi mu le.
\v 22 Bɛŋ bvûuse chiaaŋ fɛ mwɛɛ mù mbefe le munchii.
\p 
\v 23 Nlɛge lɛ Nyo kibɛɛ wù le Nyo wu kimbonɛ wu gê lɛ bɛŋ yuude bachii yi fiɛɛ le fichii. Wu gɛ̂ɛ kiyo kena bɛ muntele mwɛna mo ye yene, mu nyûme ŋgilɛ sɛŋ yi kife kì Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso Kletu lé wu gê wu tô le.
\v 24 Wu wù Nyo wù gɛ̀ tɛŋe bɛŋ, le wu wù to wu lɛme gɛh yi jɛ ye le, wu lé wu gê noo.
\p 
\v 25 Booŋ ba bwee wese, bɛŋ bûune fɛ bee le.
\p 
\v 26 Bɛŋ yɛ̂sɛ booŋ ba bwee wese besabɛŋ le bachii, bɛŋ kfûgɛ, bɛŋ shîŋɛ njɛ bamii ba Nyo.
\p 
\v 27 Njɛme nchiise lo bɛŋ le a bvuŋga bvu Tada le lɛ bɛŋ tɛ̂ɛŋ ŋwa wunɛ fɛ booŋ ba bwee wese besabɛŋ le bachii lɛ bo yù.
\p 
\v 28 Kiŋkoŋɛ ki Tada wese besabɛŋ wù Jiso Kletu ki nyûme bɛ bɛŋ.
